### Step 5: Database Query Optimization

#### [NEW] [scripts/optimize_database.sql](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/scripts/optimize_database.sql)

**Purpose:** SQL script to add performance indexes

**Indexes to Add:**
```sql
-- Optimize student queries
ALTER TABLE gibbonPerson ADD INDEX idx_status (status);
ALTER TABLE gibbonPerson ADD INDEX idx_role (gibbonRoleIDPrimary);

-- Optimize student enrollment queries
ALTER TABLE gibbonStudentEnrolment ADD INDEX idx_person (gibbonPersonID);
ALTER TABLE gibbonStudentEnrolment ADD INDEX idx_year (gibbonYearGroupID);

-- Optimize timetable queries
ALTER TABLE gibbonTTDayRowClass ADD INDEX idx_person (gibbonPersonID);
```

**Query Optimizations in API:**
1. Use `SELECT` with specific columns (not `SELECT *`)
2. Add `LIMIT` clauses everywhere
3. Optimize JOIN conditions
4. Use prepared statements (already done)

